text: geuleona geudeul ijeon-e gajeong-eul gajgo mid-eum-eul gajyeossdeon jadeul-eun geudeul egelo ijuhayeo on salamdeul-eul sa langhayeossgo geudeul-ege bepul-eojin geos eulo sigihaji anihaess-eumyeo gananhamyeonseodo jasindeulboda geudeul-eul useon daeuhayeoss-eumyeo nuguegedeun ma-eum i insaeghaji anihaess-euni ideul-i beonseonghan jadeul-ila
